<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 5:30
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='319000' id='t-319000'>And what happened?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='321000' id='t-321000'>In all this thing,</span>
