<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='338000' id='t-338000'>And so that's the case of everyone joining in.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='340000' id='t-340000'>We didn't have a strong government. We didn't have lots of doctors.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='343000' id='t-343000'>But it's everybody's job</span>
