<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 5:58
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='347000' id='t-347000'>Then AIDS came along and hit Thailand,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='349000' id='t-349000'>and we had to stop doing a lot of good things</span>
