</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 6:45
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='394000' id='t-394000'>Every ministry, even judges, had to be involved in AIDS education --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='397000' id='t-397000'>everyone -- and we said the public, institutions,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='400000' id='t-400000'>religious institutions, schools --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='402000' id='t-402000'>everyone was involved.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='404000' id='t-404000'>And here, every media person</span>
