</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 8:46
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='515000' id='t-515000'>And these were the condoms that we introduced.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='520000' id='t-520000'>One says, &quot;Weapon of mass protection.&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='522000' id='t-522000'>We found --</span>
