<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='603000' id='t-603000'>Otherwise there wouldn't be many Thais walking around today.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='606000' id='t-606000'>So it just showed you, you could do something about it.</span>
