<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='627000' id='t-627000'>but in cooperation with the business community.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='630000' id='t-630000'>Because poor people are business people</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='632000' id='t-632000'>who lack business skills and access to credit.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='635000' id='t-635000'>Those are the things to be provided by the business community.</span>
