<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='663000' id='t-663000'>And before you can borrow the money, you need to be trained.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='666000' id='t-666000'>And we believe if you want to help the poor,</span>
