<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='687000' id='t-687000'>These are some of the businesses:</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='689000' id='t-689000'>mushrooms, crabs, vegetables,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='692000' id='t-692000'>trees, fruits,</span>
